text: Lisa Mamie (born 27 October 1998) is a Swiss swimmer. She competed in the women's 100 metre breaststroke at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships. In 2014, she represented Switzerland at the 2014 Summer Youth Olympics held in Nanjing, China. ==References== Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss female swimmers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Swimmers at the 2014 Summer Youth Olympics Category:Female breaststroke swimmers
